'''''Bad Influence''''' is a [[1990 in film|1990]] [[United States|American]] film starring [[Rob Lowe]] and [[James Spader]]. In this [[film noir|noirish]] film, Spader plays a [[yuppie]] who meets a mysterious stranger (Lowe) who encourages him to explore his darker side.

==Cast==
*[[Rob Lowe]] as Alex
*[[James Spader]] as Michael Boll
*[[Lisa Zane]] as Claire
*[[Christian Clemenson]] as Pismo Boll
*[[Marcia Cross]] as Ruth Fielding

==Crew==
*Directed by [[Curtis Hanson]]
*Written by [[David Koepp]]

